snippet.title: Actor Johnny Depp rejects ex-wife's abuse claims in libel action
snippet.description:
Actor Johnny Depp accused his ex-wife, actress Amber Heard, of having extra-marital affairs and lying about him beating her up as he began libel action in a London court against a British tabloid.
